text: Mandiraja Market (Indonesian: Pasar Mandiraja) is a traditional market in the village of Mandirajakulon, Indonesia. It is one of the largest traditional markets in the Banjarnegara District. It was created by the Banjarnegara District government.Mandiraja Traditional Markets ==References== ==Other websites== * Website Resmi Kabupaten Banjarnegara Category:Street markets Category:Central Java
